WEBVTT

00:03:59.944 --> 00:04:03.904
you can very easily create
a 300-tree strong small forest.

00:04:03.944 --> 00:04:06.874
(Applause)

00:04:06.904 --> 00:04:09.238
This way of planting forests
is not just my idea,

00:04:09.262 --> 00:04:11.400
it belongs to all of us.

00:04:11.424 --> 00:04:13.720
All the papers we use,

00:04:13.744 --> 00:04:18.970
the entire process of creating
a forest, is available to everyone.

00:04:19.014 --> 00:04:25.024
By using this Kenya, Korea,
America, India, Australia,

00:04:25.539 --> 00:04:28.040
people all over the world
using the Miyawaki method

00:04:28.064 --> 00:04:29.731
are planting big and small forests.